config.text: Beaumont Urban Forest Explorer

Welcome to the

Urban Forest Explorer!


Beaumont's urban forest provides many advantages to daily life. Trees keep things shaded and cool in the summer, buffer noise from street traffic, and even help manage rain water runoff. Caring for and expanding Beaumont's urban forest is important for the overall health and livability of the city.
